===Noun===
'''ambivert''' (plural '''ambiverts''')
#A person having characteristics of both [[extrovert|extrovertion]] and [[introvert|introvertion]]. Ambiverts have the unique ability to get along equally well with introverts and extroverts, being somewhat 'in between'; they understand the needs of both types. Although they get along, ambiverts often will not tolerate extremes of extrovertion of introvertion.